Module Std.Debug

== Inox 0.1 debug/checking facade.
==
== Canonical future API:
==
==   Assert(Condition Bool)
==   Assert(Condition Bool, Message String)
==
== Assert(false) must trap/abort in debug/checking mode with a clear diagnostic.
== It is intentionally not implemented as a non-fatal PutLn wrapper. A fake
== Assert that merely prints and returns would violate Inox's mission-critical
== semantics.
==
== This module becomes executable once the compiler/runtime exposes a canonical
== trap or abort intrinsic.
